RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 31. Claiming Purse 5880. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 4 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BROOKS N BAND came again, driving. BARRIO SAN JOSE dueled, gamely. CAPITAN PIZARRO off slowly, finished well. PAPI'S ONE FOR ALL weakened. SEA RUNNER SONG failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 6F Dirt CR: 44. Allowance Purse 15200. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 4 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MANDAVLEE WARRIOR close up, dueled, up. LONDON GHOST close up, bid, dueled, gamely. PULPMASTER inside, angled out, weakened. GRACIAN improved position. CLEMENS weakened. NAVAGIO trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 56. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 4 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: TALVEZ TALVEZ dueled, prevailed. GUANAJIBO dueled, gamely. NEW MILIONAIRE gamely third. NEGOCIADOR gamely third. FABIAN GUILLERMO weakened. MAGO DE ORIENTE failed to menace. MY FAVORITE J C dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 1 1/8M Dirt CR: 71. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON THREE RACES SINCE MARCH 4 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 4 Al lowed 3 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BEACHTREASUREGIRL rallied outside, led, prevailed. MYSTICAL JUSTICE close up, grudgingly. SNOWZILLA pressed pace, lacked punch. LADY ALEXANDRIA pressed pace, weakened. SIREN'S LUCKY SONG set pace, weakened. OUR CHOICE failed to menace. NOWITNA RIVER dwelt.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 64. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON THREE RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 4 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since Janua ry 4 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CAPTAIN led throughout. POKER COCO second best. CAMPECHANO improved position. LIBRE SOY evenly. BLACK MAKUMBA improved position. SILVER PATH improved position. CHIEFICIA dropped back. FUN LOADED dropped back. SKY BRIDGE dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 6F Dirt CR: 34. Maiden Special Weight Purse 11500. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. 2# A clasf. inferior y debts Allowed 2 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: WILNELIS outside rally, drew off. HABIAQUEDECIRLO bid outside, good effort. QUEEN HERA loomed, flattened out. YOHELYS set pace, weakened. LA QUE NADIE QUISO improved position. ESPERANZA DE DOS dropped back. AMADA MIA dropped back. PATRIA MIA failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 19. Maiden Claiming Purse 6800. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. 1# A clasf. $8,000 Allowed 1 lbs. 2# A clasf. inferior y debts Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FILISTEO led, prevailed. LUCKY APOLLO finished well, short. D' ARION pressed pace, led, gave way. VIENTO VELOZ finished well. JEY GUELIN vied for lead, weakened. CONTROVERSIAL pressed pace, weakened. DEL BARRIO trailed.
